               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180506-57-person519">
                  CHRISTIAN 
                  GEORGE OCHSE
               <interp inst="t18180506-57-person519" type="surname" value="GEORGE OCHSE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-57-person519" type="given" value="CHRISTIAN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-57-person519" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Warwick-court, Holborn. On the 12th of April, about eleven o'clock, I was going along <placeName id="t18180506-57-crimeloc321">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180506-57-crimeloc321" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180506-57-crimeloc321" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-57-off319 t18180506-57-crimeloc321"></join>, a man pushed me behind near Fullwood's-rents-the prisoner met me, and snatched at my watch; the handle of my watch broke - He got the seals. I collared him - He broke from me; I collared him again, we both fell together; he got away, and ran down Southampton-buildings - I secured him there, and never lost sight of him. I am certain he is the man.</p>
               <p>
            
